    <item>
      <title>预计 2030 年香港私人财富资产将飙升至 2.3 万亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/hk-private-wealth-assets-seen-surging-to-2-3-trillion-by-2030</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博行业研究显示，香港管理的私人财富资产可能在六年内增长近一倍，达到 2.3 万亿美元，预计香港将超过瑞士，成为全球顶级跨境财富中心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/hk-private-wealth-assets-seen-surging-to-2-3-trillion-by-2030</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 24 Oct 2024 03:36:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>越南总理希望加快与中国铁路项目的合作</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/vietnam-premier-aims-to-quicken-railway-projects-with-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据越南政府网站发布的消息称，越南总理范明政希望“加快”连接越南和中国的三条跨境铁路的建设进度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/vietnam-premier-aims-to-quicken-railway-projects-with-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 24 Oct 2024 03:34:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本财务大臣就日元快速下跌发出警告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/japan-s-finance-chief-gives-warning-over-yen-s-rapid-slide</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本财务大臣加藤胜信表示，日元兑美元汇率跌至近三个月来的最低点后，他正在提高监控汇率走势的紧迫性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/japan-s-finance-chief-gives-warning-over-yen-s-rapid-slide</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 24 Oct 2024 03:17:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯称特朗普为法西斯分子，旨在加强 2024 年大选对比</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/harris-calls-trump-a-fascist-in-bid-to-sharpen-election-contrast</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯在关键摇摆州宾夕法尼亚州举行的 CNN 市政厅会议上回答提问时，向尚未决定的选民进一步强调了她的结论性陈述，即唐纳德·特朗普不适合连任第二任期，并将她的对手归类为法西斯主义者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/harris-calls-trump-a-fascist-in-bid-to-sharpen-election-contrast</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 24 Oct 2024 02:08:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本央行观察人士认为 10 月不会有变化，一半人预计 12 月会有所变化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/boj-watchers-see-no-october-move-with-half-expecting-december</link>
      <description><![CDATA[接受彭博调查的大多数经济学家表示，日本央行预计将于下周维持基准利率不变，并于12月或1月加息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/boj-watchers-see-no-october-move-with-half-expecting-december</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 23 Oct 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
