      <title>印尼再次在争议海域驱逐中国海警</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/indonesia-drives-out-china-coast-guard-vessel-in-disputed-waters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印尼海事安全局称，其拦截并驱离了一艘中国海警船，这是该船一周内第二次进入印尼领土。]]></description>
